! 20010130  GiGa v4 (Vanya Belyaev)
  a lot of major and minor modifications
   - GiGa/*.h  ONLY  interfaces and header files for "base" classes, 
               all other files now belongs to src subdirectory
   - GiGaLVolumeCnv - new converter for LVolume into G4LogicalVolume 
   - GiGaDetectorElementCnv - new converter
   - A lot of improvement in GiGaGeomCnvSvc
      o Name of G4LogicalVolume   objects is set to be  ILVolume::name() 
      o If G4VPhysicalVolume object is created during an ordinary conversion of 
        daughters volumed of mother Logical Volume, it gets the name = "MotherName#IPVolume::name()" 
        If G4VPhysical is created durion the conversion of DetectorElementObject
        it gets the name of IDetectorElement::name(). This convention allows to 
        perform an easy check and to avoid the multiple conversion of geometry.
      o It is possible to specify the "Global" magnetic field
   - implementation of GiGaBase - a useful utility for implementation of 
     PhysicsList, SensitiveDetector, MagneticField, Stepper and Action classes
     in an easy and  configurable  way 
   - Physics List business: 
      o  new "pseudo-abstract" interface IGiGaPhysList for Physics List Objects
      o  new interface for IGiGaPhysListFactory for factories, which are able to produce IGiGaPhysList Objects  
      o  implementation of templated factory GiGaPhysListFactory
      o  GiGaPhysListL - implementation of base class for any CONCRETE physics list object 
      o  GiGaPhysListGeantino - a  "minimal" Physics List (geantino), "cut&paste" from ExN01PhysicsList
      o  GiGaPhysListEm       - an "electromgnetic" Physics List, "cut&paste" from ExN02PhysicsList
      o  GiGaPhysListFull     - a  "quite extensive"(full?) Physics List, "cut&paste" from ExN04PhysicsList
      o  GiGaSvc is updated accordingly ( property: "PhysicsList", format: "Type/Name" )
   - Sensitive Detector business
      o  new "pseudo-adstract" interface IGiGaSensDet for Sensitive Detector Objects
      o  new interface IGiGaSensDetFactory for factories, which are able to produce IGiGaSensDet Objects
      o  implementation of templated factory GiGaSensDetFactory
      o  GiGaSensDet      - implementation of base class for any CONCRETE Sensitive Detector 
      o  GiGaSensDetPrint - trivial example of concrete sensitive detector implementation: 
                       no hit creation, just some printout. 
      o  GiGaGeomCnvSvc is updates accordingly. 
           "Sensitivity" is a property of Logical Volume 
           ( const std::string& ILVolume::sdName() ) in a format "Type/Name". 
   - Magnetic Field business
      o new "pseudo-abstrct interface IGiGaMagField foe Magnetic Field Object 
      o  new interface IGiGaMagFieldFactory for factories, which are able to produce IGiGaMagField Objects
      o  implementation of templated factory GiGaMagFieldFactory
      o  GiGaMagField       - implementation of base class  for magnetic field
      o  GiGaMagFieldGlobal - implementation of concrete Magnetic Field object
                        It is "trivial"  example -   just delegation to IMagneticFieldSvc. 
      o  GiGaMagFieldUniform - implementation of concrete Magnetic Field object
                         It is also "trivial"  example - just constant uniform magnetic field  
      o  GiGaGeomCnvSvs is update to incorporate these features 

